title: Uofe
description: Prince Fortem again sets out on a dangerous adventure to save his beloved, who was abducted by the evil Demon-Of-the-Tower, one of the lords of the Lava Kingdom. The prince is to cross impenetrable forests, deep dungeons, desert and snow, fight with pirates and, finally, get to the very kingdom of Lava. The game is a first-person shooter in a fairy-tale setting. The main weapon of the prince is the crossbow, but in extreme cases the sword can also go to play. Join the adventure in the magical World of Four Elements
